headline: Generac business attractive but fairly valued - Barclays
summary: Investing.com -- Barclays initiated coverage on Generac Holdings (NYSE:GNRC) Inc. with an Equal Weight rating and a $189 price target, citing an attractive business model but a stock valuation that already reflects much of the recent optimism.
